          "en": "Al-Husayn ibn Ahmad ibn Idris (may God have mercy on him) narrated to us. He said: My father narrated to us from Muhammad ibn al-Husayn ibn Abi'l Khattab, from Muhammad ibn Abi Umayr, from Ja'far al-Azdi, from Amr ibn Abi'l Miqdam. He said: I heard Abu Ja'far al-Baqir (peace be upon him) say:",
